</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: expression_extensions_schema  Entity: expression_relationship  
   <express_ref linkend="expression_extensions_schema::expression_extensions_schema.expression_relationship"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
  <ext_description linkend="expression_extensions_schema.expression_relationship">
 A general association between one expression and another.

<note>this entity is used to track casual information of relationships between expressions. For example, one critical temperature can have a reference to another just for information's sake. Formal dependency relationships shall be handled by expressions of various arity, assignment definitions or other specific definitions.
</note>
</ext_description>

